# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PG DHUNDO — FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file:  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in every value marked with  <-- REQUIRED
#   3. NEVER commit .env to Git — it is already in .gitignore
#
# VITE NOTE:
#   All variables MUST start with "VITE_" to be accessible in browser code.
#   Access them via:  import.meta.env.VITE_VARIABLE_NAME
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Backend API URL ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The full base URL of the deployed FastAPI backend. No trailing slash.
#
# LOCAL DEV:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
#
# PRODUCTION (paste your Render service URL):
#   VITE_API_URL=https://pg-dhundo-backend.onrender.com
#
VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000   # <-- REQUIRED

# ── Razorpay ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your Razorpay PUBLIC Key ID (safe to expose in browser — it's not a secret).
#
# WHERE TO GET IT:
#   • Log in at https://dashboard.razorpay.com/
#   • Go to: Settings → API Keys → Generate Test Key (or Live Key for production)
#   • Copy the Key ID (starts with "rzp_test_..." or "rzp_live_...")
#
# TEST MODE  (use during development — no real money moves):
#   VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY=rzp_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# LIVE MODE  (use in production — real payments):
#   VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY=rzp_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# ⚠  Never paste your KEY SECRET here. Only the Key ID goes here.
#
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY=rzp_test_YOUR_KEY_HERE   # <-- REQUIRED
